{"tid":1506812,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"可以點郁嗰兩個指揮官？","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:38:50.000Z","uid":222389,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"87f7e0350cc54f6cf5fd86fb0e86543da55b78bf","tid":1506812,"uid":222389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:19:36.000Z","msg":"［代po]<br />\n中國無簽Rome statute<br />\n所以icc管轄權係管唔到中國 <br />\n但係英國加拿大澳洲呢啲國家全部都有簽 <br />\nicc嘅管轄權係去到呢啲國家嘅國民 <br />\n即係話理論上嗰兩個外籍指揮官係可以被告上icc嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBXELCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBXELCM.jpg&h=1d30abc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡單啲嚟講兩個方法 第一係 經聯合國安理會 知但係中國係聯合國安理會常任理事有否決權所以行唔通 第二個方法係有協約國提出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y70CxhX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy70CxhX.jpg&h=b4e854e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下一步最重要嘅係首先要確定佢哋係咩國籍 然後可以試下直接去同嗰個國家交涉<br />\n<br />\n同樣嘅嘢亦都可以適用於任何有外國國籍嘅官員或者警察"},{"pid":"f6f3bc7e6b6d0c61d1f485d9160116cc094528da","tid":1506812,"uid":222389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n嗚哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41da3d4f345691f0177e28640c758ffc1e180e8a","tid":1506812,"uid":222389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:20:22.000Z","msg":"612<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a046dd387e076a2c11320b07aaa5ec6c8f04175","tid":1506812,"uid":222389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbe781f01a5e21916a1a9cba8fa43a4a2ff9dc7","tid":1506812,"uid":222389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdc2a6528676acbf51b6a904b47b8263df097b2","tid":1506812